how should i ratio this things?

if i have like 6 days of work

1 - day should be about yesterdey = documentation (git + doc),reviewing and tomorow =  concepts

3 - days should be about implementing developement mainly

1 - day should be about learning

1 - day should be about twiks = standardization  (celean code, sugestii), performance, small inhancements



in every step / day we should priorities what we do...some things may have a
big priority and some of them might have a small priority
